text:
I’m a Systems Software Engineer currently residing in Washington State, USA. I have contributed software to the FreeBSD project (systat -ifstat), am a core Python committer, and Apache Subversion committer. My main languages are C, C++, and Python.
I’m also a private pilot, and have my tailwheel, complex, and high-performance endorsements. I enjoy aerobatics, and have been fortunate enough to fly with Patty Wagstaff in her Extra 300 back in 2017.
I can be contacted via trent@trent.me.
